quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  21,94,"Namni mu’umina ta’ee gaggaarii irraa hojjate, hojii isaa hoonga’uun hin jiruNuti isaaf galmeessaadha"
  21,95,Ganda ishee balleessine irratti (duniyatti deebi'uun) dhorgaadha; isaan hin deebi'an
  21,96,Hanga yeroo (hidhaan) Ya’ajuujiifi Ma’ajuuj banamee isaanis tabba hunda irraan dhangala’anuutti (hin deebi'anu)
  21,97,"Waadaan dhugaas dhihaatee jiraYeroo san ijji warra kafaree akkuma banamtetti haftuudha“Yaa badii keenya! Dhugumatti, nuti kana irraa daguu keessa turre(Yoom kana qofa) inumaa miidhaa raawwattoota irraa taane\" jedhu"
  21,98,"Dhugumatti, isiniifi wantoonni isin Rabbiin ala gabbartanis qoraan (ibidda) jahannami; isin ishee (Jahannam) seenoodha"
  21,99,Isaan (taabotoonni) kunniin odoo gabbaramtoota ta’anii silaa ishee hin seenan tureHundi isaaniis ishee keessatti waaru (hafu)
  21,100,Isaaniif ishee keessatti halaaka (iyyaansa) harreetu jira; akkasumas isaan ishee keessatti hin dhaga’an
  21,101,"Dhugumatti, warra Nu irraa milkiin isaaniif dabarte, isaan sun ishee irraa fageeffamoodha"
  21,102,Sagalee ishee hin dhaga’anuIsaanis waan lubbuun isaanii jaallattu keessatti hafoodha
  21,103,(Guyyaa Qiyaamaa) naasuun guddaan isaan hin gaddisiisuMaleykonnis isaan qunnamuun “Kun guyyaa keessan kan waadaa isiniif galamaa tureedha” (jedhuun)
  21,104,"Guyyaa samii akka barreessan xalayaa (galmee) marutti marru san [yaadadhu]Akkuma uumaa duraa jalqabnetti isa deebifna(Kun) waadaa Nu irra jiruudhaDhugumatti, Nuti raawwattoota taanee jirra"
  21,105,"Dhugumatti, Nuti erga ‘Lawhal Mahfuuz’ keessatti barreessinee booda kitaabota keessatti “dachii gabroota kiyya gaggaariitu dhaalaa” barreessineerra"
  21,106,"Dhugumatti, (Qur’aana) kana keessa ergaa ga'aa ta’etu namoota (Rabbiin) gabbaraniif jira"
  21,107,Aalama hundaaf rahmata taasifnee malee (waan biraatiif) si hin ergine
  21,108,"(Yaa Muhammad!) Jedhi: “Ani wanti gara kiyyatti wahyii godhamu ‘dhugaan gabbaramaan keessan gabbaramaa tokkicha’ (kan jedhuu dha)Sila isin Muslimoota hin taatanuu ree?”"
  21,109,"Yoo gara galan “Ani ifaan ifatti isin beeksiseAni wanti waadaa isiniif galame dhihoo moo, fagoo ta’aa isaa hin beeku” jedhi"
  21,110,"Dhugumatti, Inni jecha ol fuudhamaa ni beekaWaan isin dhoksitanis ni beeka"
  21,111,Ani inni (an isinitti himu kun) mokkoroo isiniif ta’uufi qananii yeroo gabaabaa (isiniif) ta’aa hin beeku
  21,112,"(Muhammad) ni jedhe: “(Yaa) Rabbi! (Anaafi warra ana sobsiisan giddutti) dhugaan murtii godhiGooftaan keenyas Rahmaani, waan isin jettan irrattis gargaarsifatamaadha"